                {
                  "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3t72822s/manifest/annotation/p3",
                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>up the girls, and for keeping the family together since <persName>Mr<lb/>\n                    Thorps</persName> death as she has had to depend on her own means<lb/> to do so,\n                    <persName>Mr Thorp</persName> having left nothing of his own in fact<lb/> not\n                enough to pay his debts &amp; <persName>Charles</persName> will do nothing<lb/> for\n                his sisters, not even to the extent of a wedding present to<lb/>\n                <persName>Sarah</persName>. However I think they will do very well without him<lb/>\n                at all events I do not intend to let them suffer.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Many thanks to <persName>Mrs Cozens</persName> &amp; yourself for\n                the kind solicitude<lb/> expressed by you both for my health <del>And</del> which\n                has greatly<lb/> improved since my last. And I now have hopes that it<lb/> will not\n                be advisable for me to take the southern tour<lb/> heretofore contemplated.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">With kindest regards to <persName>Mrs Cozens</persName> &amp; the\n                girls, and<lb/> best wishes for the health &amp; prosperity of all</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(9)\">I remain, sincerely</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\">your well wisher</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(11)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Hanford</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p><persName>Mrs Hanford</persName> &amp; <persName>Mr Sale<add>?</add></persName>\n                send</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">kind regards</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3t72822s/canvas/p3"
                }
              ]
